title: Test Drive Unlimited Custom Soundtrack
description:
This is something of a companion to dopeman&#039;s Test Drive Unlimited upload. Herein you will find most of the original Test Drive Unlimited soundtrack (I dropped a few truly annoying tracks), plus bonus tracks from the Drive Parellel Lines soundtrack (it&#039;s mostly very awesome driving music) and I fleshed out the hip hop station with some of my own collection.

Drop these folders into your My DocumentsTest Drive UnlimitedsavegameUSERNAMERadio folder. You may have to create the Radio folder yourself.

Enjoy!
